# Topic ACLs (suggestions.md S-2).
#
# Devices (user "edgebox" in dev; per-device users in production) may only
# PUBLISH telemetry. The ingestion service may only SUBSCRIBE. Neither can
# do the other's job, so a leaked device credential cannot be used to spy
# on the rest of the fleet's traffic.

user edgebox
topic write edgebox/#

user core-ingestion
topic read edgebox/#
